quran[26{c,v,t}:
37,77,aur un ki aulaad ko aisakiya ke wohi baqi reh gay
37,78,aur peechay anay walon mein un ka zikar ( Jameel baqi ) chore diya
37,79,yani ) tamam Jahan mein ( ke ) Nooh par salam
37,80,naiko karon ko hum aisa hi badla diya karte hain
37,81,be shak woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
37,82,phir hum ne dosaron ko duubo diya
37,83,aur un hi ke pairon mein ibrahim they
37,84,jab woh apne perwar-digaar ke paas ( aib se ) pak dil le kar aeye
37,85,jab unhon ne apne baap se aur apni qoum se kaha ke tum kin cheezon ko pujte ho ?
37,86,kyun jhoot ( bana kar ) khuda ke siwa aur mabodon ke taalib ho ?
37,87,bhala perwar-digaar aalam ke baray mein tumharakiya khayaal hai ?
37,88,tab unhon ne sitaron ki taraf aik nazar ki
37,89,aur kaha mein to bemaar hon
37,90,tab woh un se peeth phair kar lout gay
37,91,phir ibrahim un ke mabodon ki taraf mutwajjah hue aur kehnay lagey ke tum khatay kyun nahi ?
37,92,tumhekiya howa hai tum boltay nahi ?
37,93,phir un ko dahinay haath se maarna ( aur torna ) shurukiya
37,94,to woh log un ke paas doray hue aeye
37,95,unhon ne kaha ke tum aisi cheezon ko kyun pujte ho jin ko khud tarashtain ho ?
37,96,halaank tum ko aur jo tum banatay ho is ko khuda hi ne pedakiya hai
37,97,woh kehnay lagey ke is ke liye aik imarat banaao phir is ko aag ke dhair mein daal do
37,98,gharz unhon ne un ke sath aik chaal chalni chahi aur hum ne un hi ko zair kardiya
37,99,aur ibrahim bolay ke mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf jaane wala hon woh mujhe rasta dukhaay ga
37,100,ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( aulaad ) ataa farma ( jo ) Saadat mandoon mein se ( ho )
37,101,to hum ne un ko aik naram dil larke ki khushkhabri di
37,102,jab woh un ke sath dornay ( ki Umar ) ko pouncha to ibrahim ne kaha ke beta mein khawab mein daikhta hon ke ( goya ) tum ko zibah kar raha hon to tum socho ke tumharakiya khayaal hai? unhon ne kaha ke abba jo aap ko hukum howa hai wohi kijiye khuda ne chaha to aap mujhe sabron mein paiyay ga
